About

Scribe is a no-nonsense lightweight IRC logger in 2 parts.
1: Ruby script to run in the background and watch your IRC channels
2: Sinatra webapp to receive messages from bot and interface with user

Setup

Copy the scribe.yml.sample -> scribe.yml and edit settings ... you can put as many rooms int he config as you need.
Open the webapp and you will be asked for a secret ... use the same secret in your scribe.yml